channel.title: Test the Interface Endpoint :: AWS Intership Report
channel.description: Get the regional DNS name of S3 interface endpoint From the Amazon VPC menu, choose Endpoints. Click the name of newly created endpoint: s3-interface-endpoint. Click details and save the regional DNS name of the endpoint (the first one) to your text-editor for later use. Connect to EC2 instance in “VPC On-prem” Navigate to Session manager by typing “session manager” in the search box
